column5: The 2013 OFC Fishing Tourney ends on December 15, 2013, so captains and teams, please make sure all your entries are in before midnight on December 15th.  Captains, please make sure you have sent in any entries that have been sent to you and check your entries page to make sure the biggest fish you have is in each category.  Good luck to all teams!!  Joey
Thanks for the reminder! Looks like we won't be able to get a whitefish, unless we get some very, very cold nights this week.
Chris we have a big cold front coming but I hope that guys be very safe thinking about going out deep as first ice is always iffy.
I'd be going shallow, but still need cold weather.
